To invite a new team member:

1. Go to https://lance-knox.netlify.app and sign in
2. Press F12 to open browser console
3. Run this script (replace name/email/role as needed):

   const userId = 'name-' + Date.now().toString(36);
   const token = crypto.randomUUID().replace(/-/g,'');
   const exp = new Date(Date.now() + 7*24*60*60*1000).toISOString();
   const users = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('ku')||'[]');
   users.push({id:userId, name:'Full Name', role:'admin', cr:[], ch:'', joined:''});
   localStorage.setItem('ku', JSON.stringify(users));
   const invs = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('ki')||'[]');
   invs.push({tok:token, uid:userId, exp:exp, used:false});
   localStorage.setItem('ki', JSON.stringify(invs));
   console.log('Token:', token);

4. Copy the token from the console output
5. Send to the new member with the invitation email and user guide

For multiple invitations at once, use the bulk script (see Team Setup manual).

Tokens expire after 7 days.
